**Closed:** #25 (mysql_*→native PDO), #26 (deploy on/off/redeploy lifecycle + gate), #28 (README PDO
section), #29 (GPL-header stamp), #44 (form elements: number/date/multiselect), #45 (POM serialize→JSON),
